{
  "title": "Velvety Peppery Lentils Stir-fry",
  "description": "A post-workout Venezuelan dish featuring brown lentils, toasting for added texture and flavor, with a hint of heat from peppercorns, suitable as a side or light meal.",
  "cuisine": "Venezuelan",
